Telkom S. Africa Will Take 3 Years on Acquisitions, Reuters Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-04-13T10:38:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/telkom-s-africa-will-take-3-years-on-acquisitions-reuters-says.html
Telkom South Africa Ltd. will look
at making acquisitions in two to three years, Reuters said,
citing Chief Executive Officer Nombulelo Moholi.  The company will fix what it already owns, the news agency
cited Moholi as saying in an interview with e.tv, a
Johannesburg-based television station.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  